subSubSection.paragraph:
Remarks. This species is similar to
Tetra heilongjiangensis
Kuang, 1995
, but can be differentiated by dorsal annuli with microtubercles (dorsal annuli smooth in
T . heilongjiangensis
), median line present (median line absent in
T . heilongjiangensis
), coxal area with granules (coxal area with short lines in
T . heilongjiangensis
).
